1. Copy the file into your folder
2. Go to the path containing sravya_robot.cpp file and then Compile and run C++ program in a Terminal using:

make sravya_robot
./sravya_robot

Enter your inputs and Type 'exit' to stop the program.

Any supported IDE can also be used to run the program.


 % ./sravya_robot
Enter your input for the Robot. Type 'exit' to stop the program:
place(1,4,south)
Placed Robot at give location:1,4,SOUTH
move
Moved robot one step towards SOUTH
move
Moved robot one step towards SOUTH
report
Robot is at location:1,2,SOUTH
 --- --- --- --- ---
